OL,6,FIt is hoped that the results will
OL,7,Fassist schools in understanding how
OL,8,Factive their students are overall and
OL,9,Fduring which parts of the school day.
OL,11,FIt is recommended that children are
OL,12,Factive for at least 30 minutes a day
OL,13,Fwhilst at school.
